@startuml
title Varierende PSU - GOMAA-inspired Subsystem Chart
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowThickness 1

actor Operator
actor "Phone User" as PhoneUser

rectangle "Varierende PSU System" {

  package "Control Subsystem" <<subsystem>> as Control {
    component "pwmTask()\n- Current measurement\n- P control\n- LEDC/PWM output" as PWMTask
  }

  package "Interface Subsystem" <<subsystem>> as Interface {
    component "interfaceTask()\n- Screen update\n- RFID scan\n- PIN handling\n- Inactivity check" as UITask
  }

  package "Web Subsystem" <<subsystem>> as Web {
    component "serverTask()\n- handleClient()\n- Login pages\n- User creation\n- Status polling" as ServerTask
  }

  package "Storage Subsystem" <<subsystem>> as Storage {
    database "SD card\nlogins.csv\ndokumentation.csv" as SDStore
  }

  package "Shared State" <<subsystem>> as SharedState {
    component "Global variables\nworkerID\nmanglerPin\nisLoggedIn\nkorrektPin\nwaitforChip\ncurrentDuty" as Globals
  }
}

package "Hardware" {
  component "PWM power stage" as PowerStage
  component "Shunt / ADC input" as Shunt
  component "TFT display" as TFT
  component "RFID reader" as RFID
  component "Capacitive keypad" as Keypad
  component "WiFi AP + HTTP client" as WiFiClient
}

Operator --> TFT : sees status
Operator --> RFID : presents tag
Operator --> Keypad : enters PIN
PhoneUser --> WiFiClient : browser access

UITask --> TFT : updates UI
UITask --> RFID : reads UID
UITask --> Keypad : reads PIN
UITask --> Globals : reads/writes
UITask --> SDStore : login lookup / log data

ServerTask --> WiFiClient : HTTP service
ServerTask --> Globals : reads/writes
ServerTask --> SDStore : create/reset users

PWMTask --> Shunt : reads current
PWMTask --> PowerStage : sets PWM duty
PWMTask --> Globals : reads/writes

SDStore -up-> Storage
TFT -up-> Interface
RFID -up-> Interface
Keypad -up-> Interface
Shunt -up-> Control
PowerStage -up-> Control
WiFiClient -up-> Web

note bottom of SharedState
Subsystems communicate mainly through
shared global state variables.
end note

note bottom of Control
Highest-priority periodic task
(currently 10 ms period).
end note

note bottom of Interface
Periodic task for local interaction
and access control.
end note

note bottom of Web
Periodic server polling task on
the second core.
end note

@enduml
